Symbol.Script_3D:
IF gs_shadow=0 THEN SHADOW OFF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
resol gs_resol * (gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2) + 8 * (gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1) PEN gs_cont_pen
!!! Posts addz legHeight*(iLegTipType>1) for vp=1 to 2 for hp=1 to 2 material frameMat prism_ 4, zzyzx-gridHeight-legHeight*(iLegTipType>1), 0, 0, 15, frameWidth, 0, 15, frameWidth, frameDepth, 15, 0, frameDepth, 15 mulx -1 addx -a next hp del 4 muly -1 addy -b next vp del 4 del 1 !!! End Of Posts
!!! Top Frame addz zzyzx-gridHeight material frameMat prism_ 10, gridHeight, 0, 0, 15, a, 0, 15, a, b, 15, 0, b, 15, 0, 0, -1,
frameWidth, frameDepth, 15, a-frameWidth, frameDepth, 15, a-frameWidth, b-frameDepth, 15, frameWidth, b-frameDepth, 15, frameWidth, frameDepth, -1 del 1 !!! End Of Top Frame
!!! Horizontal Grids add frameWidth+horGridDist, 0, zzyzx-gridHeight for hg=1 to horGridNum for hgg=1 to verGridNum+1 material frameMat prism_ 4, gridHeight, 0, frameDepth, 15, gridWidth, frameDepth, 15, gridWidth, frameDepth+verGridDist, 15, 0, frameDepth+verGridDist, 15 addy gridWidth+verGridDist next hgg del verGridNum+1 addx horGridDist+gridWidth next hg del horGridNum del 1 !!! End Of Horizontal Grids
!!! Vertical Grids add 0, frameDepth+verGridDist, zzyzx-gridHeight for vg=1 to verGridNum material frameMat prism_ 4, gridHeight, frameWidth, 0, 15, a-frameWidth, 0, 15, a-frameWidth, gridWidth, 15, frameWidth, gridWidth, 15 addy verGridDist+gridWidth next vg del verGridNum del 1 !!! End Of Vertical Grids
!!! Umbrella Holder addz umbHoldElev for huh=1 to 2 material frameMat prism_ 4, umbHoldHeight, frameWidth, 0, 15, a-frameWidth, 0, 15, a-frameWidth, frameDepth, 15, frameWidth, frameDepth, 15 muly -1 addy -b next huh del 4
for vuh=1 to 2 material frameMat prism_ 4, umbHoldHeight, 0, frameDepth, 15, frameWidth, frameDepth, 15, frameWidth, b-frameDepth, 15, 0, b-frameDepth, 15 mulx -1 addx -a next vuh del 4 del 1
addz umbHoldElev+umbHoldThk for vuc=1 to moduleNumVer if vuc=1 or vuc=moduleNumVer then umbHoldDepth = (b - 2 * frameDepth - (moduleNumVer - 1) * gridWidth) / moduleNumVer - umbHoldThk - umbHoldThk * (moduleNumVer = 1) else umbHoldDepth = (b - 2 * frameDepth - (moduleNumVer - 1) * gridWidth) / moduleNumVer endif
for huc=1 to moduleNumHor if huc=1 or huc=moduleNumHor then umbHoldWidth = (a - 2 * frameWidth - (moduleNumHor - 1) * gridWidth) / moduleNumHor - umbHoldThk - umbHoldThk * (moduleNumHor = 1) else umbHoldWidth = (a - 2 * frameWidth - (moduleNumHor - 1) * gridWidth) / moduleNumHor endif
cutform 4, 1, 1+16, 0, 0, -1, 0, frameWidth+umbHoldThk, frameDepth+umbHoldThk, 1+2+4+8+16, frameWidth+umbHoldThk+umbHoldWidth, frameDepth+umbHoldThk, 1+2+4+8+16, frameWidth+umbHoldThk+umbHoldWidth, frameDepth+umbHoldThk+umbHoldDepth, 1+2+4+8+16, frameWidth+umbHoldThk, frameDepth+umbHoldThk+umbHoldDepth, 1+2+4+8+16 addx umbHoldWidth+gridWidth next huc del moduleNumHor addy umbHoldDepth+gridWidth next vuc del moduleNumVer del 1
addz umbHoldElev material umbHoldMat prism_ 4, umbHoldHeight, frameWidth, frameDepth, 15, a-frameWidth, frameDepth, 15, a-frameWidth, b-frameDepth, 15, frameWidth, b-frameDepth, 15 del 1
for vuc=1 to moduleNumVer for huc=1 to moduleNumHor cutend next huc next vuc !!! End Of Umbrella Holder
!!! Side Cover if iCaseType=2 then for vp=1 to 2 for hp=1 to 2 material frameMat cutpolya 4, 1, 0, 0, 0, 15, frameWidth, 0, 15, frameWidth, frameDepth, 15, 0, frameDepth, 15 mulx -1 addx -a next hp del 4 muly -1 addy -b next vp del 4
addz umbHoldElev+umbHoldHeight for louv=1 to coverLouverNum material coverMat tube 6, 7, 1+2+16+32, coverThk, 0, 0, coverThk, coverLouverHeightR, 0, coverCutDepth, coverLouverHeightR, 0, 0, coverLouverHeightR-coverCutDepth, 0, 0, coverCutDepth, 0, coverCutDepth, 0, 0,
a, b, 0, 0, 0, b, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, a, 0, 0, 0, a, b, 0, 0, 0, b, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0 addz coverLouverHeightR next louv del coverLouverNum del 1
for vp=1 to 2 for hp=1 to 2 cutend next hp next vp endif !!! End Of Side Cover
!!! Legs if iLegTipType=2 then add frameWidth/2, frameDepth/2, 0
for vp=1 to 2 for hp=1 to 2 material legTipMat cone legHeight/2, min(frameWidth, frameDepth)/2, min(frameWidth, frameDepth)/2, 90, 90 addz legHeight/2 cone legHeight/2, min(frameWidth, frameDepth)/4, min(frameWidth, frameDepth)/4, 90, 90 del 1 mulx -1 addx -a+frameWidth next hp del 4 muly -1 addy -b+frameDepth next vp del 4
del 1 endif
if iLegTipType=3 then mulz -1 add frameWidth/2, frameDepth/2, -legHeight
for vp=1 to 2 for hp=1 to 2 material legTipMat cone legHeight, min(frameWidth, frameDepth)/2, min(frameWidth, frameDepth)/4, 90, 90 mulx -1 addx -a+frameWidth next hp del 4 muly -1 addy -b+frameDepth next vp del 4
del 2 endif !!! End Of Legs
Symbol.Script_2D:
pen gs_cont_pen
hotspot2 0, 0 hotspot2 a, 0 hotspot2 a, b hotspot2 0, b
POLY2_B 4, 1+4, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, frameWidth, frameDepth, 1, a-frameWidth, frameDepth, 1, a-frameWidth, b-frameDepth, 1, frameWidth, b-frameDepth, 1
!!! Horizontal Grids add2 frameWidth+horGridDist, 0 for hg=1 to horGridNum for hgg=1 to verGridNum+1 POLY2_B 4, 1+4, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, frameDepth, 0, gridWidth, frameDepth, 1, gridWidth, frameDepth+verGridDist, 0, 0, frameDepth+verGridDist, 1 add2 0, gridWidth+verGridDist next hgg del verGridNum+1 add2 horGridDist+gridWidth, 0 next hg del horGridNum del 1 !!! End Of Horizontal Grids
!!! Vertical Grids add2 0, frameDepth+verGridDist for vg=1 to verGridNum POLY2_B 4, 1+4, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, frameWidth, 0, 1, a-frameWidth, 0, 0, a-frameWidth, gridWidth, 1, frameWidth, gridWidth, 0 add2 0, verGridDist+gridWidth next vg del verGridNum del 1 !!! End Of Vertical Grids
!!! *** Background Fill fill gs_fill_type
POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, a, 0, 1, a, b, 1, 0, b, 1
Symbol.Script_1D:
eps = 0.0001
DIM stCaseType[2] stCaseType[1]=`Frame` stCaseType[2]=`Covered`
DIM stLegTipType[3] stLegTipType[1]=`None` stLegTipType[2]=`Type 1` stLegTipType[3]=`Type 2`
horGridNum = moduleNumHor * 2 - 1 horGridDist = (a - 2 * frameWidth - horGridNum * gridWidth) / (horGridNum + 1) verGridNum = moduleNumVer - 1 verGridDist = (b - 2 * frameDepth - verGridNum * gridWidth) / (verGridNum + 1)
umbHoldThk = 0.01
coverThk = 0.02 coverCutDepth = coverThk / 4 coverHeight = zzyzx - umbHoldHeight - umbHoldElev - gridHeight
coverLouverNum = int(coverHeight / coverLouverHeight) coverLouverHeightR = coverHeight / coverLouverNum
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types_RF_WMCC" parameters all
values "gs_resol" range [3,)
values "gs_detlevel_3D" `Detailed`, `Simple`, `Off` values "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0 if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then if gs_detlevel_3D = `Detailed` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Simple` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Off` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m else if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Detailed` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Simple` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Off` parameters gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D endif
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then hideparameter "gs_resol" if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow"
values "caseType" stCaseType values "iCaseType" 1, 2 if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "caseType" then if caseType = stCaseType[1] then iCaseType = 1 if caseType = stCaseType[2] then iCaseType = 2 parameters iCaseType = iCaseType else if iCaseType = 1 then caseType = stCaseType[1] if iCaseType = 2 then caseType = stCaseType[2] parameters caseType = caseType endif
values "legTipType" stLegTipType values "iLegTipType" 1, 2, 3 if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "legTipType" then if legTipType = stLegTipType[1] then iLegTipType = 1 if legTipType = stLegTipType[2] then iLegTipType = 2 if legTipType = stLegTipType[3] then iLegTipType = 3 parameters iLegTipType = iLegTipType else if iLegTipType = 1 then legTipType = stLegTipType[1] if iLegTipType = 2 then legTipType = stLegTipType[2] if iLegTipType = 3 then legTipType = stLegTipType[3] parameters legTipType = legTipType endif
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "moduleNumHor" then a = moduleNumHor * moduleWidth parameters a = moduleNumHor * moduleWidth else values "a" range[moduleWidth,] step 0, moduleWidth moduleNumHor = a / moduleWidth parameters moduleNumHor = a / moduleWidth endif
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "moduleNumVer" then b = moduleNumVer * moduleDepth parameters b = moduleNumVer * moduleDepth else values "b" range[moduleDepth,] step 0, moduleDepth moduleNumVer = b / moduleDepth parameters moduleNumVer = b / moduleDepth endif
values "zzyzx" range [umbHoldElev+umbHoldHeight+gridHeight+0.01+coverLouverHeight,)
values "moduleNumHor" range [1,) values "moduleNumVer" range [1,)
values "umbHoldElev" range[legHeight*(iLegTipType>1),) values "umbHoldHeight" range[umbHoldThk,) values "coverLouverHeight" range[coverCutDepth*2,)
if iLegTipType=1 then lock "legHeight", "legTipMat" hideparameter "legHeight", "legTipMat" endif if iLegTipType=1 then lock "gs_resol" hideparameter "gs_resol" endif if iCaseType=1 then lock "coverMat", "coverLouverHeight" hideparameter "coverMat", "coverLouverHeight" endif
